The converter is intended for importing orders and members from ShopSite to Statamic and Bison.

Place /converter on your web server (suggested location is web root). If necessary, adjust configuration in config.php

Export ShopSite orders to XML file. Upload the file (default location is /converter/orders.xml)

Point your browser to http://your-domain.com/converter

If there are no errors, the data have been migrated

MAKE SURE TO DELETE converter FOLDER AFTER IMPORT

